name: cats, mice & death
description:
A cat that needs to feed her kittens. She needs to overcome obstacles in dimensions and rodents. Help the kitten to feed her kittens!.

FACT SHEET

  • Developers Juan Deyby, Marielena
  • Release Date 12 June 2022
  • Platforms Browser
  • Price Free

FEATURES

  • Casual game
  • Only one player
  • Use a keyboard and mouse

CREDITS 

Music Production: Free sound

PS : Requires Browser with WebGL3.0 and above to run, any lower requires Hardware Acceleration to be disabled, which slows performance by a lot.
